Additionally, the use of computational methods suggests that the paper may also belong to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The analysis of similarities and differences between texts may also involve statistical modeling, making cs.CY (Computational Geometry) a possible sub-category. Finally, the use of computational methods for analyzing language may also involve deep learning techniques, making cs.DL (Machine Learning) a possible sub-category.
